      • StartMatchTwoTimesWithValidBackup

        @Test
public void StartMatchTwoTimesWithValidBackup()
        Tests the resuming of a previous match (because names of the new game match with the previous ones) Starts a match, does som actions. Then stop the match. Then creates five players with identical names (in the same order) and tests that the old match is resumed. Then does some other actions. Then stops it and creates players with the same names but in a different order. Then restarts teh match and check that it is resumed, again.
